  - Several HTML pages do not call their corresponding API endpoints
  - fetch() calls missing credentials:'include' (session cookie not sent)
  - Some pages use hardcoded http://localhost:5000 absolute URLs
  - Pages do not check session on load → no redirect to login if unauth

