  [dashboard.html]
  - On load: fetch('GET /auth/me', {credentials:'include'})
      → if 401: redirect to /pages/login.html
      → if ok: fetch('GET /auth/achievements', {credentials:'include'})
  - Render all 4 macro rings + bar chart from real API data
  - Show username from /auth/me response in header pill

  [home.html]
  - On load: fetch('GET /auth/me', {credentials:'include'})
      → if ok: show "Welcome back, {username}!" greeting
